face,
burned
brown
with
the
tropical
sun,
and
shot
with
a
thousand
wrinkles.
He
wore
white
linen
clothes,
in
true
planter
style,
with
a
cigar
between
his
lips,
and
a
large
Panama
hat
upon
the
back
of
his
