But
it
needed
all
his
cordiality
to
atone
for
the
frigidity
and
even
rudeness
of
his
wife,
a
tall,
haggard
woman,
who
came
forward
at
his
summons.
She
was,
I
believe,
of
Brazilian
extraction,
though
she
spoke
