She
did
not
attempt
to
conceal,
however,
either
then
or
afterwards,
that
I
was
no
very
welcome
visitor
at
Greylands
Court.
Her
actual
words
were,
as
a
rule,
courteous,
but
she
was
the
possessor
of
a
pair
